narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 110 05 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 110 05 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: Tom is a great professor and really focuses on each theme well, and always criticizes your work in a constructive way. I got a ton of feedback on every essay, and we had a humor section which some classes skipped over. A great choice if you're looking to write a bunch.
Take it-you need to learn to write better, even if you think you don't.
I would definitely recommend this class to another student. DO IT.
